title: The Story of 2 Unique Brothers (2 of Only 150 Known Cases)

media:group.media:title: The Story of 2 Unique Brothers (2 of Only 150 Known Cases)
media:group.media:description:
Zach and Ryan are brothers who share the same genetic disorder of which there are only 150 known cases in the world. They have the same rare condition, but their personalities are incredibly unique.
